{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with up to 8 players in this physics-based, mixed online/local multiplayer slime battling game. The goal is simple, eat food to get bigger and then eat the other players. Enjoy a wide variety of themed levels, interactive physical obstacles and dynamic abilities that combine to create unique experiences every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/Slime_Physics-wobbly.png?t=1733748854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/616_Isolated.gif?t=1733748854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slip, slop and slap around the arena with super satisfying visuals and controls that are easy to learn but hard to master </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/Scavenge_for_food-wobbly.png?t=1733748854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/616_SlimeJuice.gif?t=1733748854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eat food to grow! Body slam into slime balls to suck them up as you grow from a cute drop of slime into a massive monster</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/Food_Fighting-wobbly.png?t=1733748854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143740/extras/616_TugOfWar.gif?t=1733748854\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Latch on and drag food away to take it all for yourself, but watch out! The extra weight slows you down a